title: Latent Change on Change Between Tau Accumulation and Cognitive Decline
text:
Project Aims
Using latent change score models (lcsm), examine the associations between:

change in tau on change in pacc
change in pacc on change in tau
cross-sectional tau on change in pacc
cross-sectional pacc on change in tau

We will test these associations while covarying for baseline age, sex, years of education, and APOEe4 status.
